lass=\"keyword\">if</span>(t1==t3)k=t2;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> k=t1;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d %d\\n\"</span>,k,Calc(a,k)+Calc(b,k)+Calc(c,k));</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\tInit();</div><div class=\"line\">\tWork();</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdin</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdout</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>"}